  <description><![CDATA[<p>Nestling by the port in a corner of San Marco di Castellabate is this charming hotel which has recently added one of the best spas of the area featuring Thalassotherapy treatments. The restaurant uses organic and local produce to create wonderful delicacies accompanied by some excellent Campania wines. Keen walkers can easily reach the excellent paths of Punta Licosa, part of the Natural Park of Cilento, which is rich in perfumed Mediterranean plants and flowers and has sea views over the protected coastline. The perfect place to unwind and relax!</p>]]></description>
