  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p>Outdoor seawater pool (closed 2-4pm); small private sandy beach; wellness centre (see below); treatments and massages (local charge); fitness room; WiFi. Bathrobes and flip flops for the spa provided.</p>
<p><strong>Thalasso Spa</strong></p>
<p>The new state-of-the-art spa centre restores body and soul with a series of treatments and experiences using seawater, algae and marine muds which are known for their health-giving properties. The centre includes:</p>
<ul>
<li>Indoor/ outdoor seawater pools with hydrojets</li>
<li>‘Blue bubbles’ floating chamber</li>
<li>Salt ‘beach’ and salt sauna Finnish sauna</li>
<li>Mood showers</li>
<li>Steam rooms</li>
<li>Sea water aerosols</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
